						<summary>

						<p>The inscription has the introduction <hi rend="italic">Pugaḻmādu viḷaṅga</hi> etc. It is incomplete. It seems to record the grant of some land as <hi rend="italic">taṭṭārkāṇi</hi> at Nirandalūr to a goldsmith whose name is not clear.</p>						

