<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied></hi> pukaḻmātu viḷaṅka cayamātu virumpa nilamakaḷ nilava malarmakaḷ puṇara Urimaiyiṟ ciṟanta maṇimuṭi 
<lb n="2"/>cūṭi miṉavar nilaikeṭa villavar kulaitara Eṉaimaṉṉavar Etirmalain toṭat tikkaṉaittu n=taṉ cakkara naṭā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tti vira<hi rend="grantha">si</hi>ṅṅā<hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>ṉattu Avaṉimuḻutuṭai yāḷoṭum viṟṟiruntaru<supplied reason="omitted">ḷi</supplied>ya kovirā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>kecaripa<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi><supplied reason="omitted">rā</supplied>ṉa cakkaravarttika[ḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> ku]
<lb n="4" break="no"/>lottuṅka coḻatevaṟku <unclear>yāṇṭu</unclear> <num value="37">3 <g type="numeral">10</g> 7</num>- ḻāvatu Atirā<hi rend="grantha">jentra</hi>maṇṭala ttu meṟpākkai nāṭṭu <unclear>nira</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>n=talūrāṉa <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulottuṅkacoḻa catu<hi rend="grantha">rve</hi>ti maṅkalattu taṭṭārkkāṇi Araṅkan pomuka nā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>ṭāḻviccā <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> tirapperun=taṭṭāṉukku yāṇṭu Irupatteṭṭāvatu mutal pācūr <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> Ivaṉukkuk kāṇi<note n="421-1">Stops here.</note>
</p>

